<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 18:08:08 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>麦当劳以色列回购：屈服于抵制还是商业头脑？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/mcdonalds-israel-buyback-caving-to-boycott-or-business-sense/0000018e-b963-d712-a3df-f9eb591a0000</link><description>该连锁店表示，此举是其频繁洗牌加盟商的一部分，但批评人士表示，由于穆斯林世界的销售低迷，该公司向 BDS 抗议者让步了</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 17:40:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/mcdonalds-israel-buyback-caving-to-boycott-or-business-sense/0000018e-b963-d712-a3df-f9eb591a0000</guid></item><item><title>至少水獭正在返回以色列北部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/nature-environment/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/at-least-the-otters-are-returning-to-israels-north/0000018e-b985-db6c-a9ee-fd95a6980000</link><description>由于水资源减少和致命的道路交叉口而几乎灭绝后，对水獭粪便的调查显示，在高速公路下为它们建造的安全通道的帮助下，它们已经回到了以色列北部失踪的地区</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 17:34:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/nature-environment/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/at-least-the-otters-are-returning-to-israels-north/0000018e-b985-db6c-a9ee-fd95a6980000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府表示不会弥合与总检察长在极端正统派军队征兵豁免问题上的分歧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-says-no-bridging-gaps-with-ag-on-ultra-orthodox-army-exemption/0000018e-b92c-d8b4-a3be-fd2f473c0000</link><description>在总检察长告诉以色列高等法院，没有法律依据可以免除极端正统派人士服兵役后，政府提出了独立代表的请求。上周，一项冻结犹太学校预算的命令开始生效，学生们避免入伍</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 17:03:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-says-no-bridging-gaps-with-ag-on-ultra-orthodox-army-exemption/0000018e-b92c-d8b4-a3be-fd2f473c0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡谈到“全面胜利”。那么，以色列国防军为何要从加沙南部撤军呢？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-07/ty-article/.highlight/why-is-the-idf-withdrawing-from-southern-gaza/0000018e-b945-d712-a3df-f9ef58750000</link><description>哈马斯袭击以色列六个月后，以色列国防军将从加沙南部撤军，但内塔尼亚胡并不急于结束战争</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 16:55:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-07/ty-article/.highlight/why-is-the-idf-withdrawing-from-southern-gaza/0000018e-b945-d712-a3df-f9ef58750000</guid></item><item><title>以色列右翼抗议者大肆宣扬阴谋，度过了一个疯狂的夜晚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/a-wild-night-with-israels-conspiracy-spouting-right-wing-protesters/0000018e-b930-df26-a99e-f97fccf30000</link><description>如果以色列司法部长官邸附近的一小群示威者可信的话，那么 BDS 运动是耶路撒冷反内塔尼亚胡抗议活动的资助者之一，而且“对伤害右翼政客的人的制裁还不够” &amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 16:48:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/a-wild-night-with-israels-conspiracy-spouting-right-wing-protesters/0000018e-b930-df26-a99e-f97fccf30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 184 天：英国首相卡梅伦表示英国对以色列的支持并非无条件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-184-u-k-support-for-israel-not-unconditional-fm-cameron-says/0000018e-b967-d8b4-a3be-fd6f1aca0001</link><description>以色列国防军从加沙南部撤军 ■ 伊朗高级官员：以色列大使馆都不安全 ■ 以色列国防机构已“完成伊朗应对所需的准备” ■ 以色列代表团前往开罗进行人质释放/停火协议谈判 ■ 英国支持外交大臣卡梅伦称以色列“并非无条件” ■ 约旦河西岸枪击事件造成三人受伤 ■ 战争结束 184 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 16:38:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-184-u-k-support-for-israel-not-unconditional-fm-cameron-says/0000018e-b967-d8b4-a3be-fd6f1aca0001</guid></item><item><title>以色列司机碾压反政府抗议者，造成五人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-driver-runs-over-anti-govt-protesters-wounding-five/0000018e-b904-d8b4-a3be-fd0f24610000</link><description>一名反政府抗议者受中伤，另外四人受轻伤。反对党领袖亚伊尔·拉皮德表示，这一事件是“政府煽动的直接结果”</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 16:00:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-driver-runs-over-anti-govt-protesters-wounding-five/0000018e-b904-d8b4-a3be-fd0f24610000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方概述了反政府抗议者的法律后果和监禁判决</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-clarifies-rules-for-legal-protesting-at-saturday-nights-anti-govt-protest/0000018e-b8da-d8b4-a3be-fcdf85240000</link><description>上周二在耶路撒冷举行的抗议活动中，警察和抗议者之间的紧张关系达到了顶峰，包括辛贝特（Shin Bet）负责人罗南·巴尔（Ronen Bar）在内的领导人对此表示强烈反对，他称这次抗议活动“超出了可接受的抗议活动的规则”</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 15:01:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-clarifies-rules-for-legal-protesting-at-saturday-nights-anti-govt-protest/0000018e-b8da-d8b4-a3be-fcdf85240000</guid></item><item><title>客运价格上涨后，以色列航空公司提高货运航班价格</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/gaza-war-reduced-competition-israeli-airline-el-al-raised-cargo-flight-prices/0000018e-b800-d50a-a1bf-f86e325e0000</link><description>在以色列航空客运航班价格上涨引起以色列竞争管理局的注意后，进口商现在报告称，该公司已将货运价格提高了 50%；以色列航空表示，价格上涨反映出货运市场价格上涨；货运主管：“归根结底，这是一个供需问题”</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 14:29:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/gaza-war-reduced-competition-israeli-airline-el-al-raised-cargo-flight-prices/0000018e-b800-d50a-a1bf-f86e325e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在西岸枪击事件中受重伤，两名平民受轻伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/soldier-seriously-wounded-and-two-civilians-lightly-wounded-in-west-bank-shooting-attack/0000018e-b8ad-d8b4-a3be-fcaf02a40000</link><description>以色列军队认为，成功逃脱的恐怖分子是单独行动，正在搜寻周边地区</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 14:02:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/soldier-seriously-wounded-and-two-civilians-lightly-wounded-in-west-bank-shooting-attack/0000018e-b8ad-d8b4-a3be-fcaf02a40000</guid></item><item><title>经过四个月的战斗，以色列军队从加沙南部撤军</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-withdraws-from-southern-gaza-after-four-months-of-fighting/0000018e-b8ac-db6c-a9ee-fcbc97880000</link><description>军队在谈到即将离开汗尤尼斯的第 98 师时表示，“任何可以在那里做的事情我们都做了”。以色列国防军部队将留在北部，守卫将加沙一分为二的走廊</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 13:51:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-withdraws-from-southern-gaza-after-four-months-of-fighting/0000018e-b8ac-db6c-a9ee-fcbc97880000</guid></item><item><title>“我想明确紧迫性”：为什么这位巴勒斯坦裔美国医生放弃拜登</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-this-palestinian-american-doctor-who-came-back-from-gaza-walked-out-on-biden/0000018e-b7e5-d906-a5cf-b7f5d7260000</link><description>泰尔·艾哈迈德医生今年早些时候在加沙汗尤尼斯医院待了几周，他向《国土报》讲述了他在白宫与乔·拜登总统会面时戏剧性的退出，以及他目睹的悲剧：“你只想让它停止”你希望它立即停止&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 13:30:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-this-palestinian-american-doctor-who-came-back-from-gaza-walked-out-on-biden/0000018e-b7e5-d906-a5cf-b7f5d7260000</guid></item><item><title>当MSNBC被问及以色列对哈马斯的资助时，利库德集团部长结结巴巴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-stumbles-when-asked-on-msnbc-about-israeli-funding-for-hamas/0000018e-b82d-d50a-a1bf-f86fbf520000</link><description>政客在面对一名无情地将自己的猎物引向陷阱的敏锐记者时自掘坟墓的情况并不常见，但这正是观众在 MSNBC 的乔·斯卡伯勒 (Joe Scarborough) 采访利库德集团部长尼尔·巴尔卡特 (Nir Barkat) 时亲眼目睹的情况。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 12:33:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-stumbles-when-asked-on-msnbc-about-israeli-funding-for-hamas/0000018e-b82d-d50a-a1bf-f86fbf520000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯谋杀了我的父母。六个月后，以色列的复仇战争威胁着我们所有人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hamas-murdered-my-parents-six-months-later-israels-war-of-revenge-threatens-us-all/0000018e-b7d5-d906-a5cf-b7d55d670000</link><description>以色列人和巴勒斯坦人在加沙陷入了一场战争，这场战争既没有摧毁哈马斯，也没有释放以色列人质。那么它的真正目标是什么？我们以及世界其他国家现在可以做什么来确保这场战争的所有受害者不会白白牺牲？</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 12:19:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hamas-murdered-my-parents-six-months-later-israels-war-of-revenge-threatens-us-all/0000018e-b7d5-d906-a5cf-b7d55d670000</guid></item><item><title>辛贝特相信伊朗是向在加沙被扣为人质的以色列妇女家人送葬花圈的幕后黑手</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/shin-bet-believes-iran-behind-funeral-wreath-sent-to-family-of-israeli-hostage/0000018e-b804-d906-a5cf-ba94695c0000</link><description>寄给以色列人质莉莉·阿尔巴格（Liri Albag）家人的一封信中写道，“愿她的记忆成为祝福，但每个人都知道国家更重要”。据信她还活着。用于订购鲜花的号码与辛贝特安全部门此前曝光的伊朗影响力活动有关</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 11:24:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/shin-bet-believes-iran-behind-funeral-wreath-sent-to-family-of-israeli-hostage/0000018e-b804-d906-a5cf-ba94695c0000</guid></item><item><title>“我永远不能责怪抵制以色列艺术的人”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-04-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-never-could-blame-people-who-boycott-israeli-art/0000018e-aa74-d906-a5cf-aaf491670000</link><description>早在 2019 年以色列艺术家 Roee Rosen 被诊断出患有无法治愈的癌症之前，死亡和疾病就一直是他作品的核心。在新展览“如何隐藏自己的痛苦”中，他谈到了这个主题，尽管加沙战争才是伤害他的原因今天</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 11:23:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-04-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-never-could-blame-people-who-boycott-israeli-art/0000018e-aa74-d906-a5cf-aaf491670000</guid></item><item><title>六个月后：10 月 7 日和加沙战争如何改变了全球犹太人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article-static-ext/.premium/six-months-on-how-october-7-and-the-gaza-war-transformed-jews-across-the-globe/0000018e-6024-d27e-a7af-7aee16960000</link><description>六个月后</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 10:08:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article-static-ext/.premium/six-months-on-how-october-7-and-the-gaza-war-transformed-jews-across-the-globe/0000018e-6024-d27e-a7af-7aee16960000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队将在加沙被士兵杀害的人质坟墓上立军事墓碑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-to-place-military-tombstone-on-grave-of-hostage-killed-by-soldiers-in-gaza/0000018e-b765-d50a-a9ff-ff7fe9fb0000</link><description>去年 12 月，阿隆·沙姆里兹 (Alon Shamriz) 与另外两名人质 Yotam Haim 和 Samer Fuad El-Talalka 在加沙逃离绑架者后被枪杀</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 08:44:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-to-place-military-tombstone-on-grave-of-hostage-killed-by-soldiers-in-gaza/0000018e-b765-d50a-a9ff-ff7fe9fb0000</guid></item><item><title>四名以色列突击队员在加沙南部丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/four-israeli-commandos-killed-in-southern-gaza/0000018e-b6d1-d50a-a1bf-feff25210000</link><description>枪手从隧道中出现后，士兵们在汗尤尼斯地区搜寻恐怖分子时被杀</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 06:35:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/four-israeli-commandos-killed-in-southern-gaza/0000018e-b6d1-d50a-a1bf-feff25210000</guid></item><item><title>如果没有明确的政治目标，增加加沙援助将无助于以色列军队击败哈马斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/without-declared-goals-increasing-gaza-aid-wont-help-the-israeli-army-defeat-hamas/0000018e-b50d-dc75-afde-f5fd38960000</link><description>以色列国防军在消灭恐怖分子和销毁武器方面取得的战术成功并没有影响加沙战争的结果，如果没有中央政府的分配，增加援助的国际压力也无济于事</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 03:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/without-declared-goals-increasing-gaza-aid-wont-help-the-israeli-army-defeat-hamas/0000018e-b50d-dc75-afde-f5fd38960000</guid></item></channel></rss>